# Batter Day

Batter Day is an api for viewing and ordering products.

## Data Structures
### Users (Base Model)
+ Include Id 
+ first_name: John (string, required)
+ last_name: Smith (string, required)
+ email: example@gmail.com (string, required)
+ address: 1234 N Example ST (string, required)
+ city: Norfolk (string, required)
+ state: VA (string, required)
+ zip: 10203 (number, required)
+ phone: 402-555-5555 (string, required)
+ password: 'A2BB0A7C7BB409B09EB6E0284F622E94' (string, required) - hashed password
+ orders: [2202001034] (array) - Orders id
+ Reviews: [1234, 7851, 6344] (array)
+ Favorites: [80900100011, 80019982743] (array) - Products id

### Categories (Base Model)
+ Include Id
+ name: Cookies (string, required)
+ img: 'https://picsum.photos/200/300?random=1' (string, required)
+ products_id: [80900100011, 80019982743] (array) - Products id

### Products (Base Model)
+ Include Id
+ name: Brown Butter Cookies (string, required)
+ image: https://bit.ly/3sr9EjH (string, required)
+ price: 5.95 (number, required)
+ category: Cookies (string, required) - Categories id
+ description: Delicious chocolate cookies mixed with the nuttyness of brown butter (string, required)
+ bakeTime: Bake for 10 minutes at 350ยบ F (string, required)
+ reviews: [1234, 7851, 6344] (array) - Reviews id
+ bestSeller: false (boolean)

### Orders (Base Model)
+ Include Id
+ user: '78cc315e-6f57-43da-a414-5970a306a7cf' (string, required) - Users id
+ subtotal: 70.34 (number, required)
+ created: '2022-02-03T07:40:31.075Z' (date, required)
+ dueDate: '03-01-2022' (string, required)
+ deliveryTime: 9:40 AM (string, required)
+ products: [80900100011, 80019982743] (array,required) - products id

### Reviews (Base Model)
+ Include Id
+ product: 80900100011 (number, required) - Products id
+ user: '78cc315e-6f57-43da-a414-5970a306a7cf' (string, required) - Users id
+ rating: 4 (number, required)
+ date: '2022-02-13T17:33:21.076Z' (date, required)
+ content: These were delicious cookies (string, required)

### Favorites (Base Model)
+ Include Id
+ user: '78cc315e-6f57-43da-a414-5970a306a7cf' (string, required) - Users id
+ products: 80900100011 (number, required) - Products id

### Base Model (object)
+ createdAt: `2019-08-05T08:40:51.620Z` (string, required) - Date resource was create
+ updatedAt: `2019-08-05T08:40:51.620Z` (string, required) - Date resource was last updated

### Id
+ id: `3e836f45-5f86-4a9a-a27b-17e71b60317d` (string, required) - Unique Identifier (uuid)



# Group Users Collection


## /users
### GET
Get all the users

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Users])
    
### POST
Create a new user
+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (object)
        + first_name: John (string, required)
        + last_name: Smith (string, required)
        + email: example@gmail.com (string, required)
        + address: 1234 N Example ST (string, required)
        + city: Norfolk (string, required)
        + state: VA (string, required)
        + zip: 10203 (number, required)
        + phone: 402-555-5555 (string, required)
        + password: 'A2BB0A7C7BB409B09EB6E0284F622E94' (string, required)
+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Users)
    

## /users/{id}

+ Parameters
    + id: 'f8b97084-7569-4705-b134-158d547fc3f2' (string, required) - Users id
    
### GET
Get one user by id

+ Response 200
    + Attributes (Users)

### PUT
Update a user by id

+ Response 202
    + Attributes (Users)

### DELETE
Delete a user

+ Response 202



